Class PropertyModule

java.lang.Object
org.opt4j.core.config.PropertyModule
All Implemented Interfaces:
Module, Serializable, Comparable<PropertyModule>
public final class PropertyModule extends Object implements Module, Serializable, Comparable<PropertyModule>
The PropertyModule is a decorator for a Module that enables property methods.
